items.summary:
general poster and specific character info below

items.title: general poster and specific character info below

items.text:
I'm 15 and wondering if anyone knows were I can find casting calls for my age, I have been doing theatre performances since I was 10 and want to make the step into film and TV

thank you in advance

topComments.text:
Unless you look very young, casting directors will  usually go for a recent young looking  grad to play age 15. 
It's nearly gcse year  for you so I would pause your acting and really  concentrate on your exams because you will defo need a side hustle to pay the bills even if you do well in the industry. 
Get good gcses and A levels  (avoid Arts  A levels which are notoriously hard to get top marks and can be very frustrating if others in the group are not as committed!) to keep all options open for your future.

items.text:
CASTING CALL FOR STUDENT SHORT FILM (PAID) - AIRTIME 

Hi, we are students at Nottingham Trent University making a short film about a local live news broadcast minutes away from air where everything just keeps going wrong. The entire film will take place in one shot, or at least have the appearance it is.

沒Production date: January 2026

沒広ocation: Nottingham

汳ｰPay: Paid opportunity

沁･Production company: Nottingham Trent University (Student project)

ROLES AVAILABLE

沁ｭCharacter: Martin - The director of the morning news broadcast in *Airtime*. A crass man whose declining home life has driven him to becoming a functioning alcoholic whose grip on his own life is slipping, which is starting to affect his professional life as his apathy grows. Despite his plethora of problems, he can be an amicable personality in the right circumstances and is a skilled communicator and leader. Personality wise, he combines the jadedness of adulthood with a childlike disconnect between his actions/attitude and its effects on himself and other people around him.

汨､Age Range: 35 - 50

沁ｯType: Male Actor

沍孔thnicity: White British

沒沓ased in or able to work in Nottingham, UK

沁ｭCharacter: Bethany - The assistant director in the morning news program in *Airtime*. She is highly professional and level-headed, oftentimes having to go beyond the call of duty due to the incompetence or indifference of the people around her. Bethany is very patient and would rather move the production along and work hard than waste time arguing with Martin or other members of the crew not pulling their weight. Despite her forbearance, she is finding it more difficult to bite her tongue as time goes on.

汨､Age Range: 20 - 30

沁ｯType: Female Actor

沍孔thnicity: Open

沒沓ased in or able to work in Nottingham, UK

If anyone is interested or wants more information please DM me. 

Alternatively email me, [isaacoharefilm@gmail.com](mailto:isaacoharefilm@gmail.com)

Please include your age, headshot, and role you are applying for. We can窶冲 wait to hear from you soon!

sharedPost.text:
Artist:  Benedictus quasi Deus
Album: Out of the dark (Falco Cover))(Single)
Label: Eigenlabel
Release: 21.10.2025

Benedictus quasi Deus' Interpretation von 窶朧ut of the dark窶, das ein Falco Cover ist, ist recht ansprechend konzipiert, aber bisher nur als Youtube-Video verfﾃｼgbar. Der Musiker beginnt mit sanften Panflﾃｶtentﾃｶnen und sein Gesang kommt anfangs sehr leise herﾃｼber. Dieses verstﾃ､rkt die sehr innige Haltung. Spﾃ､ter werden die Vocals rauer. Man kann also von einem Break sprechen. Energetische Effekte bringen einen besonderen und starken Touch hinein. 

Ein starker Bass verleiht dem Song einen rockigen Flair und das vorliegende Cover ist sehr interessant aufgebaut. Falcos Grundmelodie ist zu erkennen und Benedictus quasi Deus verfremdet das Original, so dass ich es als eine sehr gute Interpretation bezeichnen kann.  

Positiv herauszustellen ist auch in der Videodarstellung der Gebrauch von einer Kerze, Explosionen und Feuer, die ein dynamisches Ambiente hervorrufen.

Youtube-Video: https://youtu.be/gfvWL6h4GKk?si=YR5U2x_QCoWfQUfy

Roman Golub 
Northern Art Music - Bodystyler Musikmagazin

Proszﾄ o wysﾅＢnie maila z imieniem i nazwiskiem, aktualnym zdjﾄ冂iem twarzy i sylwetki, wizytﾃｳwkﾄ wideo (moﾅｼe byﾄ link), opisem doﾅ孩iadczenia, wiekiem oraz wzrostem na adres [marzena.casting@gmail.com](mailto:marzena.casting@gmail.com) z nazwﾄ roli w tytule maila (FOTOGRAF, MODELKA, SﾄТIADKA). Oferta non-profit.

沁ｬ CASTING 窶 Gﾅﾃ展NA ROLA W HISTORYCZNYM FILMIE 沍ｾ

Szukamy dziewczyny w wieku 15窶21 lat do gﾅづｳwnej roli w polskim filmie fabularnym osadzonym w XVII-wiecznej wsi. Film porusza tematy walki o sprawiedliwoﾅ崙, solidarnoﾅ嫩i i odwagi w trudnych czasach wojny i gﾅＰdu.

箝 Kogo szukamy?

* Dziewczyna w wieku 15窶21 lat
* Naturalna, wyrazista, gotowa do intensywnej pracy filmowej
* Mile widziane osoby bez doﾅ孩iadczenia 窶 liczy siﾄ charyzma i emocjonalna prawda

**ZgﾅＰszenia:**

Wyﾅ嬪ij prosimy na 沒ｧ **juliarokietek@gmail.com**

* Imiﾄ i nazwisko
* Wiek
* Numer telefonu
* Email
* Kilka aktualnych zdjﾄ卞

Nie przegap okazji, by staﾄ siﾄ czﾄ卩嫩iﾄ wyjﾄtkowego projektu!

items.text:
**沒｣ CASTINGAUFRUF 窶 Komparsen gesucht (Berlin) | Filmakademie Baden-Wﾃｼrttemberg**

Hallo zusammen!
Wir drehen gerade ein Filmprojekt der **Filmakademie Baden-Wﾃｼrttemberg** ﾃｼber die inspirierende Geschichte des Berliner Basketballspielers **Maodo Lo** 窶 und wir freuen uns riesig ﾃｼber eure Unterstﾃｼtzung! 泗圭nAlle, die mitmachen, werden natﾃｼrlich **im Abspann genannt**.

Wir suchen **kurzfristig Komparsen** fﾃｼr mehrere Szenen in Berlin:

**沐ｹ DONNERSTAG, 04.12 窶 Clubszene**

沒 **Maaya Club Berlin**
泄 **11:30 窶 13:30 Uhr**
汨 **Partyoutfit**, junge Erwachsene (ca. 18窶30)
Wir brauchen eine lebendige Clubatmosphﾃ､re 窶 kommt gerne auch mit Freunden!

**沐ｹ FREITAG, 05.12 窶 Jugendliche (16窶19 Jahre)**

沒 **Marzahn (genaue Adresse nach Anmeldung)**
泄 **13:15 窶 15:30 Uhr**
Wir drehen eine Szene aus Maodos Jugend und freuen uns ﾃｼber alle Jugendlichen aus Berlin, die spontan Lust haben!

**沐ｹ SONNTAG, 07.12 窶 Vernissage / Atelier-Szene**

沒 **Kunstschule Berlin**
泄 **12:00 窶 14:00 Uhr**
汨､ **Alter egal**
Fﾃｼr eine Kunst-Vernissage suchen wir Menschen, die einfach Lust auf ein paar Stunden Setluft und Kreativ-Atmosphﾃ､re haben.

**Wichtiges fﾃｼr euch:**
* Es handelt sich um ein **studentisches Projekt der Filmakademie Baden-Wﾃｼrttemberg**
* **Keine Gage**, aber:
笨費ｸ Verpflegung
笨費ｸ Dank im **Abspann**
笨費ｸ Schﾃｶnes Set-Erlebnis
* Ihr helft uns enorm dabei, diese Berliner Erfolgsgeschichte authentisch zu erzﾃ､hlen 笶､ｸ十n
Wenn ihr Zeit habt, schreibt uns einfach kurz eine DM mit:
**Name + Alter + welche Szene(n) ihr kﾃｶnnt**.
Gerne auch Freunde mitbringen!

Vielen Dank euch 窶 wir freuen uns riesig auf euch!
沁ｬ笨ｨ

沁ｬ CASTING 窶 Gﾅﾃ展NA ROLA W HISTORYCZNYM FILMIE 沍ｾ

Szukamy dziewczyny w wieku 15窶21 lat do gﾅづｳwnej roli w polskim filmie fabularnym osadzonym w XVII-wiecznej wsi. Film porusza tematy walki o sprawiedliwoﾅ崙, solidarnoﾅ嫩i i odwagi w trudnych czasach wojny i gﾅＰdu.

箝 Kogo szukamy?

* Dziewczyna w wieku 15窶21 lat
* Naturalna, wyrazista, gotowa do intensywnej pracy filmowej
* Mile widziane osoby bez doﾅ孩iadczenia 窶 liczy siﾄ charyzma i emocjonalna prawda

**ZgﾅＰszenia:**

Wyﾅ嬪ij prosimy na 沒ｧ **juliarokietek@gmail.com**

* Imiﾄ i nazwisko
* Wiek
* Numer telefonu
* Email
* Kilka aktualnych zdjﾄ卞

Nie przegap okazji, by staﾄ siﾄ czﾄ卩嫩iﾄ wyjﾄtkowego projektu!

KRAKﾃ展, poszukiwani na 7 i 8 grudnia

Do filmu krﾃｳtkometraﾅｼowego z wﾄtkiem AI realizowanego w Krakowie w dniach 7 i 8 grudnia (niedziela i poniedziaﾅＦk) szukamy

Aktora do gﾅづｳwnej roli mﾄ冱kiej FOTOGRAF 35-45 LAT (7 i 8.12 )

Aktorki do roli ﾅｼeﾅгkiej MODELKA 20-25 lat (8.12 pierwsza poﾅＰwa dnia)

Aktorki do roli epizodycznej SﾄТIADKA 35-40 lat (7.12 pierwsza poﾅＰwa dnia)

Film powstaje w ramach ﾅ孩ietlicy filmowej, ale planujemy dla niego rﾃｳwnieﾅｼ dystrybucjﾄ festiwalowﾄ. Proszﾄ o wysﾅＢnie maila z imieniem i nazwiskiem, aktualnym zdjﾄ冂iem twarzy i sylwetki, wizytﾃｳwkﾄ wideo (moﾅｼe byﾄ link), opisem doﾅ孩iadczenia, wiekiem oraz wzrostem na adres [marzena.casting@gmail.com](mailto:marzena.casting@gmail.com) z nazwﾄ roli w tytule maila (FOTOGRAF, MODELKA, SﾄТIADKA). items.text:
Rﾃｸget pﾃｸlse og kartofler

CASTING CALL

For upcoming Non-Union Series, ANCIENT BODIES SEASON 2.

Looking for 

BIPOC (Black, Indigenous, and people of colour) Male with long dark Hair, 35-40, Athletic Build (NO TATTOOS PLEASE)

Non-Union Only
Rate: $200 per day
Manitoba Residents Only (MUST have SIN #) 
Filming in Winnipeg and the surrounding areas December 11 to 19. 
Must have full day and evening availability 

Please email info@oafilmstudio.com with the subject line: 
BIPOC Male long hair_YOUR NAME

Send the following info:
- Full Name
- Age
- Gender
- Ethnicity
- Height
- Phone
- Email Address
- State that you are non-union and a Manitoba resident with a SIN# and work permit
- Your availability from December 11-19 (Must be available all day and evening)
- State if you have tattoos
- Do you have your own transportation or a reliable ride?
- If you have any acting or performance experience, let us know (Speaking, SOC, Background, Theatre, Public speaking, Social Media). No experience is alright.
- 2 Current (TAKEN DAY OF SUBMISSION) Photos (1 selfie & 1 Full Body Shot)

Please share!

#Winnipeg #winnipegcastingcall #WinnipegActing
Onalee Ames Film Studio 
150 Stafford St, Winnipeg, MB

items.text:
CASTING CALL 窶 STARFARM 

We窶决e casting fun, stylish young women (15窶25) for an unscripted eco-reality series!

AI is taking over the world. Replacing jobs, replacing people, reforming industries. They are humanity's greatest creation yet our ultimate competition. Now, an unscripted eco-reality series featuring 10 young women, learning to live on a completely remote and self-sustainable farm - across the dirt road, lies another self-sustained farm; run by AI. Will they survive or thrive? Will they change the future for the next generation of girls, by proving something woman-powered can be more fruitful than something AI-powered?

Do you have :
* 
**STRONG SENSE OF PERSONAL STYLE AND CREATIVE CONFIDENCE**
* 
**PASSION FOR FASHION, ART, FILM, TV, MUSIC VIDEOS OR DIGITAL CONTENT**
* 
**LOVE FOR ANIMALS, OR AN INTEREST IN SOCIAL/ENVIRONMENTAL CAUSES**

Think: The Simple Life x Ready Player One

Filming in BAY AREA, remote filming roles open too

Nationwide applicants encouraged to apply (travel & accommodations provided).

Total Pay: US$1,750 (est. 5 days of work)

TO APPLY:

Email themadelynx@gmail.com

Subject: *STAR FARM 窶 Your Name, Age*

Include: Name, age, location + recent photo (headshots appreciated, not required) + short intro.

## **Casting Breakdown: *****OUROBOROS***

A Psychological Horror film. The Fourth Film from Pineal Dreams Productions.

窶弩hen a young couple suffer the pain of a miscarriage; they retreat to a cottage in the woods to try and heal. Unfortunately they quickly discover that you can never run away from your trauma窶兔n
**沁 Lead Roles**

**AMAIA**

**Female | Playing age: 20-30 | Ethnicity: Open**

 **Description:** A young woman, grief-stricken, haunted by a recent miscarriage. Intelligent, emotionally complex, volatile, and deeply human. Fluctuates between tender vulnerability and violent dissociation.

 **Performance notes:** Requires a wide emotional range 窶 subtle detachment, raw grief, moments of horror, as well as serenity towards the end.  Appears in nearly every scene.

 **Comparable roles:** Charlotte Gainsbourg (*Antichrist*), Essie Davis (*The Babadook*), Jennifer Connelly *(Requiem for a Dream), *Isabelle Adjani *(Possession)*

This is a dual-role as they will also be playing the character of Amaia窶冱 Doppelganger

**AMAIA'S DOPPELGANGER **

**Female | Same actor as Amaia preferred**

 **Description:** An uncanny mirror of Amaia 窶 at times gentle, at times mocking or malevolent. Not a "villain" but an emotional specter. She represents Amaia窶冱 true opinion of herself, and pulls at her mental fragility to attempt to make her finally give in to her pain.

 **Performance notes:** If dual casting is not possible, physical resemblance and matched acting style are key. The role is symbolic and dreamlike.

 **Type:** Similar movement to Amaia, but with a more 窶惑loaty窶 and ethereal feel to it.

The nature of a dual role would suit an actress who really wants a challenge - as well as the maximum amount of screen time for any character in the film. Hopefully, a brilliant showcase role for talent who want to establish themselves as a critically respected performer, as they will be carrying the vast bulk of the film窶冱 emotional core.

We aim to film a bulk of the filming in one five-day block, with three scenes needing filming elsewhere. We anticipate filming will require ten days, with one day of ADR needed for additional dialogue/audio fixes.

We know it窶冱 frustrating when actors dangle around for months between shoots, so will be aiming to avoid that. We anticipate all filming to be completed in a 2 month period.

PAID - A minimal fee. Which can be discussed upon application. This is our fourth short-film, and the first we窶况e offered payment for. It was a late decision, as we appreciate experience doesn窶冲 pay the rent. However, being a tiny, self-funded studio, it is a relatively small amount.

All food and transport - and accommodation, if needed - also covered.

The film cannot be released by us until payment has been completed. That窶冱 our promise to you.

**DONN**

**Male | Playing age: 30-40 | Ethnicity: Open**

**Description:** Amaia窶冱 partner. Kind, supportive, but emotionally shut down. A man attempting to cope through suppression - a misguided attempt at stoicism as he believes she must be strong to support Amaia - whose quiet unraveling becomes key to the resolution.

 **Performance notes:** Understated emotionality. Requires physical performance (injury, crawling, etc.) and strong presence in silence.

 **Comparable roles:** Michael Fassbender (*Shame*), Mads Mikkelsen (*Another Round*), Javier Bardem *(Mother!)*, Harry Dean Stanton *(Paris, Texas)*

Filming block will be the same as Amaia窶冱. Five-day block (Hopefully), as well as shoots at just three other locations.Ten days of filming maximum, but this could always change if re-shoots are necessary, and one day of ADR work will be required.

We know it窶冱 frustrating when actors dangle around for months between shoots, so will be aiming to avoid that. We anticipate all filming to be completed in a 2 month period.

PAID - A minimal fee. Which can be discussed upon application. This is our fourth short-film, and the first we窶况e offered payment for. It was a late decision, as we appreciate experience doesn窶冲 pay the rent. However, being a tiny, self-funded studio, it is a relatively small amount.

All food and transport - and accommodation, if needed - also covered.

The film cannot be released by us until payment has been completed. That窶冱 our promise to you.

**汨･ Supporting Roles -**

**THE UMBRA**

**Male | Playing age: ANY | Tall, slender, distinctive presence | Ethnicity: Open**

 **Description:** A silent manifestation of trauma that watches over and manipulates events 窶 a mythic observer of Amaia窶冱 trauma. Symbol of death, memory, or fate.

 **Performance notes:** No dialogue for a vast majority of the script, though requires a sequence of some very carnival-esque dialogue. Face never seen. Must convey gravitas, mystery, and quiet threat through stillness and gaze.

 **Type:** Dancer, mime, or physical performer backgrounds welcomed. Could even opt for the possibility of a physical performer, and a separate voice-actor. So any voice-actors interested, please feel free to contact us.

Similar Roles: Doug Jones (Pan窶冱 Labyrinth), Tim Purcell (The Babadook), Javier Botet (Slenderman)

The Umbra appears in the Cottage and scenes surrounding it, all of which will be filmed during the scheduled five-day filming block.

There will also be one additional day, in which you will be required for a single scene that takes place in a different location.

Re-shoots are of course always possible, and will be needed for one ADR session for dialogue provided during an animated sequence.

PAID - But a smaller fee than Amaia/Donn as will be required for less days.  This can be discussed upon application. We aim to film a bulk of the filming in one five-day block, with one scene needing filming elsewhere. We anticipate filming will require tsix days, with one day of ADR needed for additional dialogue/audio fixes.

We know it窶冱 frustrating when actors dangle around for months between shoots, so will be aiming to avoid that. We anticipate all filming to be completed in a 2 month period.

The film cannot be released by us until payment has been completed. That窶冱 our promise to you.

We are a very small studio, and this is our fourth short. However, our mantra has always been a 窶碗uality over quantity窶 approach. We take great pride in not just making a film, but really thinking it through on a technical level. We appreciate classic and arthouse cinema, and are far more interested in making a good film than red carpet events.

Our three shorts so far have been screened at over 20 festivals, picking up around 14 awards - including two IMDB qualified awards. (best actor for Jackson Wright in Inside The Abyss). Our latest film has seen our lead - Tash Morley - pick up three awards. We aim for this to be our best film yet.

If interested in the roles, please contact me directly via the Pineal Dreams Instagram page. My own personal profiles - both Joshua Mouliniﾃｩ (Facebook/Instagram). Or Email me directly on [Moulinie23@gmail.com](mailto:Moulinie23@gmail.com)

We hope to hear from you all very soon!

items.text:
Vom Filmset ins echte Leben, Sergio Klee und Christian Weiﾃ歹 sprechen ﾃｼber Sicherheit, Wahrnehmung und Setkultur 

Wenn Verﾃ､nderung den Blick schﾃ､rft 

In diesem Teil erzﾃ､hlt Sergio Klee, wie persﾃｶnliche Entwicklung die eigene Prﾃ､senz am Set verﾃ､ndert. Er beschreibt, wie innere Anspannung weicht, wenn man versteht, woher Nervositﾃ､t wirklich kommt. Durch die Reflexion seines eigenen Weges zeigt er, wie Selbstkritik lauter sein kann als jedes Lob und weshalb Sicherheit erst entsteht, wenn man sich selbst erkennt statt sich zu verstecken. 

Wahrnehmung, Ego und die Kunst, nichts persﾃｶnlich zu nehmen 

Sergio schildert eine Situation, in der er an einem Set offen ﾃ､uﾃ歹rte, wo er sich wohlfﾃｼhlt, und plﾃｶtzlich in kritische Blicke lief. Er erklﾃ､rt, wie schnell Menschen neutrale Aussagen bewerten und warum das Ego immer eine Wertung sucht, auch wenn keine da ist. 

Von Atmosphﾃ､re, Respekt und Kleinigkeiten mit grosser Wirkung 

Die Episode zeigt, wie unterschiedlich Drehtage wirken kﾃｶnnen. Sergio vergleicht Setkulturen, Catering, Umgangsformen und kleine Gesten, die den Unterschied zwischen distanziert und familiﾃ､r ausmachen. Seine Erfahrungen bei Formaten wie Kﾃｶln 50667, Alles was zﾃ､hlt, Barbara Salesch und Ulrich Wetzel machen deutlich, wie stark Wertschﾃ､tzung das eigene Gefﾃｼhl von Zugehﾃｶrigkeit prﾃ､gt und warum sich manche Orte sofort richtig anfﾃｼhlen. 

Reinwachsen in Ablﾃ､ufe und Rﾃ､ume, bis die Kamera lﾃ､uft 

Sergio beschreibt, wie man bei jedem neuen Projekt zuerst fremd wirkt, dann Orientierung findet und schlieﾃ殕ich ankommt. Vom ersten Guten Tag im Bﾃｼro ﾃｼber Kostﾃｼm und Maske bis zur laufenden Kamera zeigt er, wie viel Sicherheit in Wiederholung und Vorbereitung steckt. Das Gesprﾃ､ch ﾃｶffnet einen seltenen Einblick in die leisen Momente vor dem Take, in denen man begreift, dass man dazugehﾃｶrt. 

Zu mir, Christian Weiﾃ歹 

Ich bin Christian Weiﾃ歹, Medienunternehmer, Content Creator und Inhaber der Karrideo Image- und Eventfilmproduktion aus Kﾃｶln. Ich entwickle Bewegtbildformate, erzﾃ､hle Geschichten fﾃｼr Unternehmen, Organisationen und Persﾃｶnlichkeiten und kenne als Darsteller beide Seiten der Kamera. 

Abonniere den Kanal, like das Video, teile deine Gedanken in den Kommentaren und besuche mind_body_coach_ auf Instagram fﾃｼr weitere Impulse von Sergio Klee. 

Christian Weiﾃ歹 / Karrideo Imagefilm-Produktion / Karrideo Imagefilm-Produktion - Zuschauer, Auftraggeber, Partner

items.summary:
Vom Filmset ins echte Leben, Sergio Klee und Christian Weiﾃ歹 sprechen ﾃｼber Sicherheit, Wahrnehmung und Setkultur 

Wenn Verﾃ､nderung den Blick schﾃ､rft 

In diesem Teil erzﾃ､hlt Sergio Klee, wie persﾃｶnliche Entwicklung die eigene Prﾃ､senz am Set verﾃ､ndert. Er beschreibt, wie innere Anspannung weicht, wenn man versteht, woher Nervositﾃ､t wirklich kommt. Durch die Reflexion seines eigenen Weges zeigt er, wie Selbstkritik lauter sein kann als jedes Lob und weshalb Sicherheit erst entsteht, wenn man sich selbst erkennt statt sich zu verstecken. 

Wahrnehmung, Ego und die Kunst, nichts persﾃｶnlich zu nehmen 

Sergio schildert eine Situation, in der er an einem Set offen ﾃ､uﾃ歹rte, wo er sich wohlfﾃｼhlt, und plﾃｶtzlich in kritische Blicke lief. Er erklﾃ､rt, wie schnell Menschen neutrale Aussagen bewerten und warum das Ego immer eine Wertung sucht, auch wenn keine da ist. 

Von Atmosphﾃ､re, Respekt und Kleinigkeiten mit grosser Wirkung 

Die Episode zeigt, wie unterschiedlich Drehtage wirken kﾃｶnnen. Sergio vergleicht Setkulturen, Catering, Umgangsformen und kleine Gesten, die den Unterschied zwischen distanziert und familiﾃ､r ausmachen. Seine Erfahrungen bei Formaten wie Kﾃｶln 50667, Alles was zﾃ､hlt, Barbara Salesch und Ulrich Wetzel machen deutlich, wie stark Wertschﾃ､tzung das eigene Gefﾃｼhl von Zugehﾃｶrigkeit prﾃ､gt und warum sich manche Orte sofort richtig anfﾃｼhlen. 

Reinwachsen in Ablﾃ､ufe und Rﾃ､ume, bis die Kamera lﾃ､uft 

Sergio beschreibt, wie man bei jedem neuen Projekt zuerst fremd wirkt, dann Orientierung findet und schlieﾃ殕ich ankommt. Vom ersten Guten Tag im Bﾃｼro ﾃｼber Kostﾃｼm und Maske bis zur laufenden Kamera zeigt er, wie viel Sicherheit in Wiederholung und Vorbereitung steckt. Das Gesprﾃ､ch ﾃｶffnet einen seltenen Einblick in die leisen Momente vor dem Take, in denen man begreift, dass man dazugehﾃｶrt. 

Zu mir, Christian Weiﾃ歹 

Ich bin Christian Weiﾃ歹, Medienunternehmer, Content Creator und Inhaber der Karrideo Image- und Eventfilmproduktion aus Kﾃｶln. Ich entwickle Bewegtbildformate, erzﾃ､hle Geschichten fﾃｼr Unternehmen, Organisationen und Persﾃｶnlichkeiten und kenne als Darsteller beide Seiten der Kamera. 

Abonniere den Kanal, like das Video, teile deine Gedanken in den Kommentaren und besuche mind_body_coach_ auf Instagram fﾃｼr weitere Impulse von Sergio Klee. 

Christian Weiﾃ歹 / Karrideo Imagefilm-Produktion / Karrideo Imagefilm-Produktion - Zuschauer, Auftraggeber, Partner

Hallo ihr Lieben,

ich arbeite an einem Projekt, in dem ich Menschen interviewe, die mit unsichtbaren oder wenig bekannten Krankheiten leben 窶 also Erkrankungen, die man nicht auf den ersten Blick sieht, die aber trotzdem den Alltag stark beeinflussen.

Mir ist wichtig, diesen Menschen eine Stimme zu geben: zu zeigen, was sie erleben, wie sie sich fﾃｼhlen und was sich in unserer Gesellschaft vielleicht verﾃ､ndern sollte.

Wenn du selbst betroffen bist oder jemanden kennst, der mit einer solchen Krankheit lebt und offen darﾃｼber sprechen mﾃｶchte, melde dich gerne bei mir.
Das Gesprﾃ､ch kann auf Wunsch anonym stattfinden.

Ich freue mich ﾃｼber jede Nachricht, jedes Vertrauen und jede Geschichte 窶 ob groﾃ oder klein.

Liebe Grﾃｼﾃ歹
Polly

items.text:
Location: Berlin

Shooting: mid-January

None paid (student project) + food + footage reel

ROLE HELEN (Lead, playing age 23-30)

Helen is the daughter of Hades, living in the mortal world in isolation.

She窶冱 observant, emotionally detached on the surface, but with a complex inner world.

Her energy is quiet, intense, and unpredictable; she feels outside of humanity while desperately

studying it.

She is not a stereotype 窶徭trong female lead窶.

She is layered, morally grey, dry, curious, bitter, vulnerable, and intimidating without trying.

A character who barely shows her emotions but feels everything deeply.

This role requires:

笳 strong subtle acting

笳 microexpressions

笳 comfort with psychological + mystical scenes

笳 ability to play someone who is always scanning her surroundings

笳 comfort acting opposite horror elements (no gore, more psychological/supernatural)

No previous fantasy experience needed, just strong emotional control and complexity.

All ethnicities welcome.

ABOUT THE PROJECT 

This is a 30-minute TV pilot for my graduation project and a proof-of-concept.

The tone is similar to The Sandman, Pan窶冱 Labyrinth, and Only Lovers Left Alive; dark, poetic,

mythological, grounded in emotional realism.

The story explores:

笳 Mythology incorporated into modern Berlin

笳 Identity and isolation

笳 Power structures

笳 Neurodivergent perception

笳 The horror of being watched by the divine

Helen is the center of this world.

We offer a complex role with depth and high-quality footage for your acting reel. As stated

before, this is a proof-of-concept pilot episode. The goal is to apply for further funding and production support in 2026 and continue the series.

REQUIREMENTS

笳 Based in Berlin or able to travel.

笳 Availability for shooting in mid-January.

笳 Comfortable with night scenes and horror tones.

笳 Able to commit to rehearsals in December.

TO APPLY!!

Send to: celia.t@catalyst-students.com

笳 Recent headshot or clear photo.

笳 Showreel (if available).

笳 Your age + where you are based.

items.text:
Hallo Zusammen,

mein Name ist Willi, ich bin 30 Jahre alt, arbeite als Senior Management Consultant bei einer internationalen Steuerberatungs- und Wirtschaftsprﾃｼfungsgesellschaft, bin nebenbei Unternehmer 窶 und trage seit meiner Kindheit eine groﾃ歹 Leidenschaft in mir: Film & Schauspiel.

Schon damals haben mich Geschichten, komplexe Charaktere und starke Bilder fasziniert. Wﾃ､hrend meines Studiums durfte ich bereits an einem Independent-Filmprojekt mitwirken, und dieses Feuer ist ﾃｼber die Jahre immer grﾃｶﾃ歹r geworden. Jetzt ist fﾃｼr mich der Zeitpunkt gekommen, mich vor der Kamera auszuprobieren und diesen Weg zu verfolgen.

Ich beginne aktuell mit hochwertigem Schauspielunterricht, unter anderem bei Lehrern, die an renommierten Universitﾃ､ten in den USA ausgebildet wurden.

Ich liebe es, mich tief in Rollen hineinzudenken, Charaktere authentisch umzusetzen und sie exzellent performen zu lassen. Hierbei bin ich sehr selbstkritisch, reflektierend, detailverliebt und habe hohe Ansprﾃｼche an mich selbst. Auch fﾃｼr Szenenbild und Atmosphﾃ､re habe ich ein gutes Gespﾃｼr 窶 ich gehe vollkommen in kreativer Arbeit auf.

Daher wﾃｼrde ich mich sehr freuen, in spannenden Projekten mitzuwirken 窶 gerne auch No-Budget und in 窶朦ebenrollen窶, denn das ist meine groﾃ歹 Leidenschaft.

Wenn ihr Unterstﾃｼtzung sucht, meldet euch sehr gerne bei mir. Ich freue mich auf den Austausch und darauf, gemeinsam Geschichten zum Leben zu erwecken.

Beste Grﾃｼﾃ歹,

Willi

Do you have experience working with children and young people aged 6-18? Do you have a passion for musical theatre and dancing, singing and acting? Are you looking for an opportunity to combine your skills and interests to develop young people in a fun and professional setting? Then PQA Haywards Heath is just the place for you!

Due to the success of our growing academy, The Pauline Quirke Academy of Performing Arts (PQA), a leading provider of weekend performing arts training, is currently recruiting MUSICAL THEATRE TEACHER for their Academy in Haywards Heath on Saturday mornings and/or afternoons.

We are searching for fun, engaging and passionate individuals looking to bring lots of exciting and innovative ideas to our Musical Theatre module. If you are passionate about learning, the performing arts and making a positive impact on the lives of young people, we would be delighted to hear from you!

PQA follows safer recruiting. An enhanced DBS on the update service will be required and can be arranged. Applicants must be 18+.

To apply please email your CV with a cover letter explaining why you would be the ideal candidate for this role. Please send these direct to Principal Florence on florence.tingley@pqacademy.com.

We look forward to hearing from you!

For upcoming Non-Union Series, ANCIENT BODIES SEASON 2.

Looking for 

Male, Caucasian, Age 35-50, Bald/Balding with a Beard 

Non-Union Only
Rate: $200 per day
Manitoba Residents Only (MUST have SIN #) 
Filming in Winnipeg and the surrounding areas December 11 & 12. 
Must have full day and evening availability 

Please email info@oafilmstudio.com with the subject line: 
Balding Male_YOUR NAME

Send the following info:
- Full Name
- Age
- Gender
- Ethnicity
- Height
- Phone
- Email Address

- Do you have your own transportation or a reliable ride?
- If you have any acting or performance experience, let us know (Speaking, SOC, Background, Theatre, Public speaking, Social Media). No experience is alright.

**Szukam modelki na zasadzie TFP  Gliwice/Katowice ( ﾅ嗟ﾄsk )  **

 

   Szukam paﾅ ktﾃｳre nie krﾄ冪ujﾄ siﾄ wﾅＢsnego ciaﾅＢ i chciaﾅＢby mieﾄ ciekawﾄ pamiﾄtkﾄ w postaci klimatycznych zdjﾄ卞.  Wiem jak bardzo jest waﾅｼna akceptacja wﾅＢsnego ciaﾅＢ bo przez to teﾅｼ moﾅｼemy inaczej funkcjonowaﾄ. Przez takie zdjﾄ冂ia moﾅｼna rﾃｳwnieﾅｼ tego dokonaﾄ. Sesja w gﾅづｳwnej mierze jest jako taki motywator.

 

Poszukuje kobiety w **wieku od 30 **lat nie koniecznie z doﾅ孩iadczeniem pozowania,  na zasadach Tfp mieszkajﾄcej w Gliwicach lub okolicach Zabrze czy Katowice najdalej. Posiadam na wyposaﾅｼeniu mini studio z kilkoma tﾅＢmi oraz lampami. Mam rﾃｳwnieﾅｼ duﾅｼy wybﾃｳr kostiumﾃｳw i gadﾅｼetﾃｳw do wykorzystywania. Gﾅづｳwny motyw do kobieta: Piﾄ冖na i drapieﾅｼna! Sama sesja trwa przewaﾅｼnie od 1,5h do 2h w zaleznoﾅ嫩i od motywﾃｳw.

** **

**Temat 1 窶 窶倪僵obieta mafii 1930窶吮**

Postaﾄ kobiety osadzona w 1930 roku w roli bogatej kobiety, ktﾃｳra trudni siﾄ gangsterstwem. Przewidziane sﾄ ujﾄ冂ia m.in. przy stoliku na ktﾃｳrym sﾄ pieniﾄdze, wino, rewolwer. TﾅＰ jest wydrukowane w formie muru, cegieﾅ. Motyw sensualny.

 

**Temat 2 窶 窶倪儻ampirzyca w baroku 1700窶吮**

Postaﾄ kobiety ubrana najpierw w suknie czarnﾄ oraz peleryne z kapturem. Do tego czarna dﾅＶga peruka oraz czarne paznokcie. W kolejnym etapie sesji motyw sensualny.

 

**Temat 3 窶 窶倪僖uchy lasu窶吮**

Postaﾄ kobiety ubrana w wianek i w pelerynﾄ z otwartym przodem. W dﾅＰni ma zakrwawiony sierp. Usta czarne oraz paznokcie.

 

**Temat 4 窶 窶倪僵leopatra窶吮**

Postaﾄ kobiety z czarna perukﾄ w stylu Kleopatry. W prawej recﾄ trzymac bﾄ囘zie berﾅＰ Anubisa a w drugiej rﾄ冂ﾄ ksiﾄ冏ﾄ umarﾅＺch. Na biodrach bﾄ囘zie mieﾄ jedynie klasyczne odzienie z 2 czﾄ卩嫩i. Na klatce piersiowej zaﾅＰﾅｼony bﾄ囘zie napierﾅ嬾ik zﾅＰty.

 

https://www.maxmodels.pl/lukus_wielki2

**Zapraszam na stronﾄ Facebook ﾅ「kasz Magiera 窶 Fotografia**

SHARING PAID OPPORTUNITY 

I窶冦 Jude, casting with Liz Lewis Casting Partners, and I wanted to share a current project we窶决e working on for Metamucil.

For this particular project, we are actually looking for real Metamucil users, ages 45窶60, with no professional acting or performing experience. While we know this community is full of talented actors, we wanted to share here in case you might know friends, family members, or people in your network who could be a great fit.

It窶冱 a nationwide search. The shoot location is still being finalized and may be Austin, or possibly Mexico or Canada. If travel is required, production will cover all travel and accommodations.

Compensation is $500 per shoot day, plus $3,400 for 1-year usage, all media.

**Participants cannot have any professional performing experience, including paid acting, dancing, or singing work (union or non-union). **

items.text:
CASTING CALL 窶 Independent Short Film (LONDON)

We are casting for an upcoming student short film exploring obsession, ambition, and the dark side of the ballet world.

Production: Student film via The American University of Rome

Director: Maxine Sutton

Cinematographer: Georgia Blackson

Shooting Dates: December 12窶19

ROLES

NATASHA (Lead)

Female, 18窶28

Ballet-trained (advanced preferred)

Must convey vulnerability, intensity, and psychological depth

Strong acting, presence, and physical performance required

Slavic accent preferred.

Pay: 250竄ｬ flat rate for entire production

RUDOLPH

Male, 25窶40

Dance experience preferred

Embodies both beauty and cruelty 窶 a man who inspires awe, fear, and complete submission.

Slavic accent preferred.

Pay: 250竄ｬ flat rate for entire production

SYNOPSIS

Natasha, a talented but tormented ballerina, navigates a high-stakes audition that tests the limits of her physical and psychological endurance. As she strives for perfection under the watchful eye of the enigmatic Rudolph, the line between reality and terror begins to blur, forcing her to confront the true cost of ambition.

TO APPLY

Please complete the audition form and send it, along with a headshot, to: maxineclairesutton@gmail.com

The @dead_zero_feature is officially LIVE and will run until the 31st Jan 2026!

This film has evolved so much since we started working on it last November and with just 35 mins left to shoot I promise you that fans of Action, Horror and Zombies will be blown away by this unique, creative and original storytelling沽酒沁･

If you support Independent Film and are a Horror Fan then please donate and spare what you can as well as share to your networks.

The more people that find our page, our film and story the faster we can get filming again

Thank you, on behalf of myself and the entire Dead Zero team 衍ｷ沁ｬ

The link is in my bio and @dead_zero_feature also 沐予n
https://www.indiegogo.com/en/projects/leedonaldson/dead-zero---action-horror--zombies-feature-film

Lee Don Productions Ltd

沒 **Location:** Melbourne, VIC
沒 **Casting Date:** TBC
沁･ **Shoot Type:** Short Film
汳ｰ **Compensation:** Paid
泓｣ **Language:** Slovak (Preference given to Slovak or Czech actors, though familiarity with Slavic languages is sufficient.)

A tense, atmospheric psychological short film set in Czechoslovakia, following a young woman haunted by visions of an imposing KGB spy as she searches for the truth behind her past.

**ROLES AVAILABLE**

沁ｭ **ZUZANNA**
*Female Presenting | 18窶25*
Outspoken, rebellious, and driven by strong beliefs. Her world fractures as paranoia surrounding her father grows into a spiralling psychological descent.

沁ｭ **FILIP**
*Male Presenting | 40s窶50s*
Worn down by years under an oppressive regime. Emotionally numb but deeply devoted to giving his daughter the freedom he never had.

沁ｭ **JOZEF**
*Male Presenting | 30s窶50s*
A chilling, ever-present KGB spy with a disturbing confidence and sinister smile. An almost otherworldly force silently stalking the story窶冱 edges.

**PROJECT TONE**

A moody, slow-burning psychological journey blurring memory and paranoia.
Rooted in Cold War-era tension, the film explores identity, fear, and the fragile bond between a father and daughter as reality begins to fracture.

Hallo liebe Freunde der Musik

Am 05.12.2025 erscheint unser Song HIMMEL AUF ERDEN auf Spotify und allen anderen Musik-Streaming-Platformen.

Hﾃｶrt gerne mal rein, erzﾃ､hlt es weiter und rockt das Sofa.

Himmel auf Erden 

Du warst der Himmel auf Erden, ich der Regen, der verwirrt auf uns fﾃ､llt.

Eine Liebe, die nicht verstanden, auf wunderbare Weise gelebt und ausradiert wird.

Dieser Rocksong symbolisiert eine Reise durch Hﾃｶhen und Tiefen, mal laut, mal leise,

vom Winde verweht, in Gedanken versunken, intensiv gelebt, nehme ich dich mit... pack den Rucksack voller Erinnerung und komm mit!

 Eure DiMiKA CRUNCH-POPﾂｮ

items.text:
Hey zusammen 汨欺n
ich teile das hier, weil ich weiﾃ, wie hart unser Weg manchmal ist. Viele von uns geben alles, spielen gut und werden trotzdem nicht wirklich gesehen. Vielleicht hilft Dir das hier ein Stﾃｼck weiter.

Ich habe einen kostenlosen 7 Tage E Mail Kurs erstellt. Jeden Tag bekommst Du eine kleine ﾃ彙ung, die Dir sofort etwas bringt und die Du ganz entspannt in Deinen Alltag einbauen kannst. Enthalten sind auch hilfreiche Tipps zu Castern, Agenturen und vielem, was uns Schauspielerinnen und Schauspieler wirklich beschﾃ､ftigt.

Nach den 7 Tagen bekommst Du ein Jahr lang einmal pro Woche kurze Impulse zu Schauspiel, Prﾃ､senz, Mindset und auch Sichtbarkeit aus meiner eigenen Arbeit vor und hinter der Kamera.

Kurz zu mir, damit Du weiﾃ殳, wer das hier teilt:

Ich bin Roberto aus Mﾃｼnchen

沁ｭ international mehrfach ausgezeichnet als Schauspieler, Autor, Regisseur und Produzent
沒ｽｸ CEO der Lucky Eagle Production GmbH
沛 Jurymitglied beim FilmHaus Berlin
沍 arbeite seit Jahren in internationalen Film und Serienprojekten

Ich arbeite unglaublich gern mit Schauspielerinnen und Schauspielern und teile das Wissen, das mir selbst auf meinem Weg wirklich geholfen hat.

Wenn Du magst, findest Du hier den Kurs und ein Video, in dem ein paar meiner Mentees erzﾃ､hlen, wie sie meine Arbeit erlebt haben:

汨 kurs.nextstagecoaching.de

Vielleicht hilft es Dir oder jemandem aus Deinem Umfeld. Gib es gerne weiter, wenn es jemand brauchen kann 笘ｺｸ十n
Und denk immer daran
Du bist genug. Genau jetzt. 洵ｶ

Roberto

Position: (Aerialist, Acrobat, Juggler 窶 performing shows at various hotels)
Contract Period: 1 May 窶 31 October 2026
Monthly Net Salary: From 竄ｬ1,000 - 1500竄ｬ (depending on experience, skills, and performance)
Employment Type: Swiss contract or self-employed freelancer

Venues: 4笘 and 5笘 hotels located on Kos, Crete, or Rhodes Island, Greece

Terms and Benefits
 窶｢ 1窶2 weeks of free rehearsals prior to the contract start date, depending on the candidate窶冱 progress in learning choreography
 窶｢ One day off per week
 窶｢ 1窶2 performances per day( 1hour show )
 窶｢ Free accommodation and board at each hotel where performances take place, including meals in the main restaurant and beverages
 窶｢ Accident, pension, and social insurance coverage included
 窶｢ 竄ｬ300 travel bonus reimbursed with the final salary for six-month contracts
 窶｢ Free airport transfer upon arrival in Greece
 窶｢ Free internet and laundry services
 窶｢ Work uniforms and costumes provided
 窶｢ Company car available for work-related purposes
 窶｢ Additional performance bonus available at the end of the contract
 窶｢ Potential for career growth within the company and opportunities for contract renewal

Palmera Team

items.text:
We are casting for the 2026 Weird and Wonderful festival which will run between March 3rd and March 8th.

窶彜ardines窶 follows five sardines as they bicker over life's meaning and their purpose in the world. 

We are looking for 5 actors of any age or look who can comfortably play off of each others comedic timing.

If you are interested in auditioning for a role please send a self tape that you feel fits the criteria via we transfer / any other downloadable link to:

Seanrobinsonfreelance@gmail.com

Self tapes are due by 31st December and the cast will be contacted by the new year.

Please note: this is a 20 min play and will be part of a three play evening. A profit share will be paid.

**ARU Record** poszukuje aktora z dojrzaﾅＺm, niskim gﾅＰsem do odegrania postaci **Gustava** z serii ***Metal Family***! Postaﾄ pojawia siﾄ w dwﾃｳch odcinkach, a jeden z nich mamy juﾅｼ niemal ukoﾅczony - brakuje nam tylko Gustava.
## Wymagania:
> 
* Mikrofon **dobrej** jakoﾅ嫩i.
* Dobre warunki akustyczne (brak pogﾅＰsu / echa).
* Wiﾄ冖sze doﾅ孩iadczenie z aktorstwem lub fandubbingiem.
* Terminowoﾅ崙.
* Dobra dykcja.

W celu zgﾅＰszenia siﾄ zapraszam do mnie na pv!
EDIT:
Chﾄ冲nych zapraszam na serwer Discord - ARU Record [https://discord.gg/CM8PjSVgjX](https://discord.gg/CM8PjSVgjX)

sharedPost.text:
Szukam starszej, sympatycznej Pani z Krakowa, ktﾃｳra chciaﾅＢby wziﾄﾄ udziaﾅ w krﾃｳtkim, ﾅ孩iﾄtecznym spocie reklamowym o Szlachetnej Paczce. 沍歃n
Chodzi o wzruszajﾄcﾄ scenﾄ: wspﾃｳlna rozmowa na ﾅＢwce, trochﾄ ciepﾅＢ, trochﾄ ﾅ孩iﾄtecznej magii窶ｦ a na koniec symboliczne podzielenie siﾄ opﾅＢtkiem. 沁笨ｨ  

Zdjﾄ冂ia bﾄ囘ﾄ realizowane w przyjemnej, spokojnej atmosferze, a caﾅＰﾅ崙 ma piﾄ冖ny i szlachetny przekaz.

Jeﾅ嬪i znacie kogoﾅ 窶 babciﾄ, ciociﾄ, sﾄsiadkﾄ 窶 ktﾃｳra mogﾅＢby siﾄ odnaleﾅｺﾄ w takiej roli, bardzo proszﾄ o kontakt. 笶､ｸ十n
Dziﾄ冖ujﾄ!

items.text:
**CASTING CALL FOR A 10-MIN SHORT FILM**
Hi everyone! We窶决e seeking local actors for a neorealist short film shooting in late January in Vancouver. The film is intended for 2026 festival submissions.

**Logline:**

A college student volunteers on a visual-assist app to help an elderly man in his small apartment, unaware that a quiet glitch has turned their private calls into a public stream.

**Production Details**

窶｢ Location: Vancouver, BC

窶｢ Shoot Window: Late January 窶 Early February 2026 (TBD)

窶｢ Genre: Neorealist Drama

窶｢ Non-Union / Volunteer

窶｢ Meals + IMDb credit provided

**ROLES**

**MAYA 窶 Female, 19窶24 (Open Ethnicity)**

Quiet, inward, emotionally guarded.
Minimal dialogue; performance driven by micro-reactions and natural handheld close-ups.
Must be comfortable with subtle, restrained acting.
Grounded student under stress 窶 *Wendy & Lucy*, *Never Rarely Sometimes Always* tone.

**LEON 窶 Male, 65窶80 (Open Ethnicity)**

Soft-spoken, solitary, dignified.
Partially visually impaired; actor need not be visually impaired but must portray limited vision naturally.
Understated physicality: small gestures, hesitation, lived-in presence.

**TO APPLY**

Please send the following to **seetogetherfilm@gmail.com**
Subject: **窶彜EE TOGETHER 窶 MAYA窶** or **窶彜EE TOGETHER 窶 LEON窶**
窶｢ Recent headshot
窶｢ Short introduction (video or written)
窶｢ Availability (Jan窶擢eb 2026)
窶｢ Any naturalistic acting samples (if available)

We will cast people first through self-tapes.

Thank you!

sharedPost.text:
FB friends, please, I need your help urgently!
I窶况e lost my engagement ring and I窶冦 devastated. This ring is incredibly important to me 窶 not only emotionally, but also because I struggle with anxiety and panic attacks, and having it with me helps keep me calm. I窶冦 truly begging for your help.

If anyone finds it, please hand it in to the real school receptionist or message me directly. Any help at all means the world to me.

I believe it may have fallen somewhere around Graphisoft Park (1031 Budapest, Zﾃ｡hony utca 7). I窶冦 not sure exactly where it slipped off. My route was: I traveled from Nyugati, took bus 9, transferred at Flﾃｳriﾃ｡n tﾃｩr to bus 106 toward Kaszﾃ｡sdﾅｱlﾅ ﾃｺt, then walked from Kaszﾃ｡sdﾅｱlﾅ to Auchan Mall and onward to IBS Business School.

This is my ring. Please, if you窶况e seen it or picked it up, let me know. I窶冦 really heartbroken and desperate. Thank you to everyone who even takes the time to read this. 汳避泗十n
FB barﾃ｡taim, kﾃｩrlek, sﾃｼrgﾅ壮en szﾃｼksﾃｩgem van a segﾃｭtsﾃｩgetekre!
Elvesztettem az eljegyzﾃｩsi gyﾅｱrﾅｱmet, ﾃｩs teljesen ﾃｶssze vagyok tﾃｶrve. Ez a gyﾅｱrﾅｱ hihetetlenﾃｼl fontos szﾃ｡momra 窶 nemcsak ﾃｩrzelmileg, hanem azﾃｩrt is, mert szorongﾃ｡ssal ﾃｩs pﾃ｡nikrohamokkal kﾃｼzdﾃｶk, ﾃｩs a gyﾅｱrﾅｱ segﾃｭt megnyugodni. Kﾃｩrlek titeket, tﾃｩnyleg kﾃｶnyﾃｶrgﾃｶm a segﾃｭtsﾃｩgﾃｩrt.

Ha valaki megtalﾃ｡lta, nagyon kﾃｩrlek, adjﾃ｡tok le az iskola recepciﾃｳjﾃ｡n vagy ﾃｭrjatok nekem ﾃｼzenetet. Bﾃ｡rmilyen segﾃｭtsﾃｩg nagyon sokat jelentene.

ﾃ喩y gondolom, valahol a Graphisoft Park kﾃｶrnyﾃｩkﾃｩn (1031 Budapest, Zﾃ｡hony utca 7) eshetett ki. Sajnos nem vettem ﾃｩszre pontosan, hol tﾃｶrtﾃｩnt. Az ﾃｺtvonalam: Nyugati felﾅ鼠 jﾃｶttem, a 9-es busszal, majd Flﾃｳriﾃ｡n tﾃｩrnﾃｩl ﾃ｡tszﾃ｡lltam a 106-os buszra Kaszﾃ｡sdﾅｱlﾅ ﾃｺt felﾃｩ. Onnan gyalog mentem az Auchanba, majd tovﾃ｡bb az IBS Business Schoolig.

Ez a gyﾅｱrﾅｱm. Kﾃｩrlek titeket, ha lﾃ｡ttﾃ｡tok vagy megtalﾃ｡ltﾃ｡tok, szﾃｳljatok. Nagyon el vagyok keseredve ﾃｩs kﾃｩtsﾃｩgbeesett vagyok. Kﾃｶszﾃｶnﾃｶm mindenkinek, aki elolvassa. 汳避泗
